Subject: Spoilers Galore for Avengers Endgame - ADDITION Errata
Description:
SPOILER ALERT 

If you are a fellow Marvel Comics Universe Geek and you have seen the latest movie, Avengers: Endgame, then this is the space to come and discuss everything and anything about the movie!  
This event will allow spoiler-filled discussions about Avengers: Endgame. 

If you have not seen Avengers: Endgame, than this is not the panel you are looking for. 

We strongly advise attendees to be aware that by chosing to attend this event, they are chosing to enter an Avengers: Endgame  Spoiler Zone! 


Speakers include:Angel Garrison, Ben Leach - Track: Media - Duration: 1 hour
